nodes.text: Panark was a  Human male Jedi Master stationed on Tython during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.

Panark appears only in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic as his character was cut from the game. He was originally going to appear in the Jedi Consular's story on Tython. Panarks's file can be found on Jedipedia.
